      "raw_text": "Articles Of incorporation were\nfiled today with the county auditor\nannouncing the formation of the\nSix Mile Hydraulic Placer Mining\n,ompany, with capital stock of\nS1,000,000, and G. M. Delameter,\nB. ]. Weeks and Alfred j. Carr as\ntrustees.\n\n\nThe Spokane and New York Land\ncompany has also been Incorporate\ned. Papers filed indicate a capital\nstock of 100000, and John Sargin-\nson, j. H. Tilsley and M. H. White\nhouse as incorporators and trust\naes."
